{"tid":1276351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"777 『九唔搭八』唔理市民的訴求","createTime":"2019-07-02T02:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:42:35.000Z","uid":223482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f264ea02b49434eb60efc361f16cd6b0b6a55e58","tid":1276351,"uid":223482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">777：<br />\n100,200萬市民示威遊行 ＝ 無回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n          衝擊立法會 泛民立法會議員要求同你傾 ＝ 好忙好！無時間！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n         衝擊完立法會 有制服的暴徒清場完 ＝強烈譴責示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n陳志全批評林鄭月娥以忙為由拒見泛民 憂再刺激示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466093-20190701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466093-20190701.htm&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=beb3de40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466093-20190701.htm&h=dc7754b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466093-20190701.htm</a><br />\n『在立法會內仍有示威者留守，部分立法會議員亦留在立法會議事廳，包括民主黨許智峯、議會陣線區諾軒，及人民力量陳志全。陳志全批評，行政長官林鄭月娥以很忙為理由，拒絕接見泛民主派議員，他又擔心會刺激部分示威者。』<br />\n<br />\n林鄭：未經調查就不檢控示威者是違背法治<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353855&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=b566ccfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353855&h=91e4bf9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353855</a><br />\n『行政長官林鄭月娥凌晨四時與政務司司長張建宗，保安局局長李家超及警務處處長盧偉聰在警察總部見傳媒，她強烈譴責有示威者以極暴力方式衝擊立法會。』<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥強烈譴責目無法紀行為 對違法行為追究到底<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466129-20190702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466129-20190702.htm&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=acfc16b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466129-20190702.htm&h=4ae17f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466129-20190702.htm</a><br />\n『她形容，這些是目無法紀行為，嚴重影響香港法治價值，她對此感到十分憤慨及痛心，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">亦予以強烈譴責，她相信市民亦有同感，她表示，警方對整日暴力行為一直表現克制，但當局會對違法行為必須追究到底。</span></span></strong>』<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔好意思呀特首，以你的角度來睇小弟應該唔係你心目中的香港市民。小弟認為政府同你果種垃圾精英主義的傲慢、囂張的態度，完全忘記左公務員係市民的公僕的原意，一直都係做造成整件事的原故。由你帶領的政府到現在還可以認為自己無任何的錯誤，「撒回」與「暫緩」在字面上已經有不同的意思及解釋，更加不用在司法覆核的法庭上的解釋！<br />\n</span><br />\n李家超：小心別有用心的人士破壞社會安寧<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353856&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=ffffbb8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D353856&h=83511073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=353856</a><br />\n<br />\n警方金鐘清場後截查往旺角小巴 在立會大樓內蒐證<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466124-20190702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466124-20190702.htm&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=1f936d83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466124-20190702.htm&h=585fdc2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466124-20190702.htm</a>"}]}